welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Lake Arbor! This charming city is known for its scenic lake and welcoming community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Lake Arbor has to offer during your visit. Welcome to our beautiful city!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves primarily domestic flights operated by American Airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal B/C
terminals.description: Terminal B/C at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves primarily domestic flights operated by Delta, United, and other airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Simply select 'DCA Free WiFi' from your device's network options and follow the prompts to connect.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Potomac Airfield Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Potomac Airfield Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Tipton AAF Airport handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Lee Airport handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport. It houses all the major airlines and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is a satellite terminal connected to the main terminal. It primarily serves domestic flights and offers a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is a satellite terminal connected to the main terminal. It primarily serves international flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport. Simply connect to the network and accept the terms and conditions to access the internet.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Montgomery County Airport caters to private and chartered flights.
